data.text:
Fubar 2

The story starts in Calgary where the boys are tired of trying to give'r while barely scraping by, when their old buddy and party leader, Tron hooks them up with jobs in Fort McMurray. Before long they are rolling in dough and good times. Terry starts dating Trish, a local waitress, and things get serious in a hurry. Meanwhile, Dean is playing up the part of the cancer survivor.
